title: AirServer 7.0.1 [k'ed]
description:
Say Hello to AirPlay + Google Cast 

AirServer is the most advanced screen mirroring software receiver for Mac and PC. It allows you to receive AirPlay and Google Cast streams, similar to an Apple TV or a Chromecast device. 

Turns your Mac into a universal mirroring receiver, allowing you to mirror your device's display using the built in AirPlay or Google Cast; one by one or simultaneously to AirServer (patent pending). 

Users can mirrror or cast their screen from any AirPlay or Google Cast compatible device such as an iPhone, iPad, Mac, Android or Chromebook. Windows and Linux platforms are also supported using the screen casting sender built into the Google Chrome browser. 

Intel, 64-bit processor 
OS X 10.8 or later 
OS X 10.9 required for YouTube streaming 
AirPlay sending devices must be on the same WiFi network
